high_descs: Make a right and then hang a left to reach the fridge.
Take out the apple from the fridge that is farthest to the right.
Turn right to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the apple in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk to the kitchen island.
Set the apple down on the kitchen island counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an apple from the fridge in the microwave to set down on the kitchen island counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead, then veer left to the the black fridge.
Pick up the red apple in the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the stove and microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn around and walk ahead, then left to the table.
Place the apple on the table to the left of the fork and right of the rightmost pencil.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the stove and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Pick up the chilled apple from the right side of the middle shelf inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn around, walk to the white stove on the left, and look up at the microwave.
Put the apple inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the green table on the left.
Put the heated apple on the middle of the table to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a table.
